---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Mission"
  description="E5 Enclave builds sovereign institutional infrastructure. Two missions: The Mission of Record and The Public Mission."
>

  <section class="section section--compact">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <span class="section-header__label">What E5 Is</span>
      <h1 class="display display--lg">Sovereign institutional infrastructure.<br/><span class="text-gold">Built by the lineage. For the lineage.</span></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <span class="body body--xs text-gold">I. The Mission of Record</span>
          <h2 class="heading heading--lg">A think tank convening a Coalition of the Willing.</h2>
          <p class="body body--lg">
            E5 Enclave is a lineage-led think tank convening a Coalition of the Willing
            to build the institutions, evidence systems, collaborative platforms, and
            community projects needed to advance the future of the lineage.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="body body--xs text-gold">II. The Public Mission</span>
          <h2 class="heading heading--lg">From Liberty City to the nation.</h2>
          <p class="body body--lg">
            From Liberty City to the nation, E5 builds the evidence, institutions, farms,
            schools, businesses, media, and policy tools our communities need to repair,
            rise, and govern their future.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--elevated">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-header__label">III. The Method</span>
      <h2 class="heading heading--lg">Agentic-first. Human-directed. Built to outlast cycles.</h2>
      <p class="body body--lg" style="max-width: 700px;">
        Operated by an agentic-first staff &mdash; AI agents under human direction &mdash;
        producing institutional-scale output from a deliberately lean operating team.
        E5 does not chase grants. E5 does not chase trends. E5 builds what lasts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Five Tenets -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-header__label">Doctrine V</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">Five institutional values.<br/>The center holds.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="tenets">
        <div class="tenet">
          <span class="tenet__num">01</span>
          <h3 class="tenet__title">Empirical Integrity</h3>
          <p class="tenet__desc">Decisions grounded in dual-source-verified evidence. What is measured cannot be dismissed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tenet">
          <span class="tenet__num">02</span>
          <h3 class="tenet__title">Sovereign Capacity</h3>
          <p class="tenet__desc">Communities own their data, their institutions, and their futures. We coordinate; we do not absorb.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tenet">
          <span class="tenet__num">03</span>
          <h3 class="tenet__title">Black-First</h3>
          <p class="tenet__desc">Built by and for the lineage. Coalition allies strengthen the work. The center holds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tenet">
          <span class="tenet__num">04</span>
          <h3 class="tenet__title">Radical Transparency</h3>
          <p class="tenet__desc">Substantial research published openly. Operating model in plain language. Records made public.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tenet">
          <span class="tenet__num">05</span>
          <h3 class="tenet__title">Intergenerational Accountability</h3>
          <p class="tenet__desc">Built for the people who will inherit it. We are stewards, not owners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--elevated cta-section">
    <div class="container container--narrow" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2 class="heading heading--lg">This is what we build.<br/><em class="text-gold">See what we've built.</em></h2>
      <div style="margin-top: var(--s-6); display: flex; gap: var(--s-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/programs/" class="btn btn--primary">View Programs</a>
        <a href="/record/" class="btn btn--secondary">Read the Record</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--s-10);
    }

    .two-col p {
      margin-top: var(--s-3);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s-8); }
    }

    .tenets {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--s-5);
    }

    .tenet {
      padding: var(--s-6);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      transition: border-color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .tenet:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-border-gold);
    }

    .tenet__num {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-weight: var(--weight-display);
    }

    .tenet__title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin: var(--s-3) 0 var(--s-2);
    }

    .tenet__desc {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-secondary);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    .cta-section em {
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
